item.title: CVE-2013-0202|2024-08-06T14:18:09.399Z -- owncloud -- owncloud
item.description: Cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in ownCloud 4.5.5, 4.0.10, and earlier allows remote attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML via the action parameter to core/ajax/sharing.php.
